methods.set:
A RowSetter that will set a value obtained from a JsonRecord as indicated in the
 record by the key. The setter and the value it sets will be matched to the type of the
 column.

:param record: io.deephaven.kafka.ingest.JsonRecord
:param key: java.lang.String
:param setter: io.deephaven.tablelogger.RowSetter

text:
Provides a String-typed set method to call a RowSetter set method and populate it with a
 value from a JsonRecord.
